description:
Enjoy this big and colorful match-3 and choose between 15 fun and challenging game modes! Assemble missing puzzle parts in classic mode, fight hordes of zombies in Zomboball mode, destroy malignant sea creatures, take part in a car race, sink enemy ships, pass through numerous mazes, avoid falling stones by exploding bombs, stop chemical reactions or solve position and logical puzzles by collecting balls of same color. You can play without time limits and enjoy the game in Relax mode. See if you can earn all 35 achievements.
